{"tid":175911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【支持法國警方執法】法國警破門射殺支那男","createTime":"2017-03-27T22:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T09:47:40.000Z","uid":37661,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20568246ea49b2a89774028c90eb54d94b312e4d","tid":175911,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T22:44:40.000Z","msg":"法國警破門射殺華裔男<br />\n中國駐法國大使館昨通報，巴黎19區一名中國人前晚因與法國警察發生衝突被打死，使館要求法警方盡快查明真相，公正處理。<br />\n<br />\n 當地華文媒體報稱，劉姓死者57歲，來自浙江青田縣溫溪鎮，與5名子女同住，當時多名警察突然破門槍擊死者；亦有人稱劉某醉酒與鄰居爭執，有警員到場後被劉持剪刀刺傷。  <br />\n（節錄）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/cntw/article/1524817/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E8%AD%A6%E7%A0%B4%E9%96%80%E5%B0%84%E6%AE%BA%E8%8F%AF%E8%A3%94%E7%94%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkej.com%2Fdailynews%2Fcntw%2Farticle%2F1524817%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25B0%2584%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E8%258F%25AF%25E8%25A3%2594%25E7%2594%25B7&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=60a4e291\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/cntw/article/1524817/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E8%AD%A6%E7%A0%B4%E9%96%80%E5%B0%84%E6%AE%BA%E8%8F%AF%E8%A3%94%E7%94%B7</a>"},{"pid":"caef1afd573d98c55df7d1477072a01616cc1905","tid":175911,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T22:53:56.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf062780f0e88d374f050a8b570386bdb413778b","tid":175911,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T22:54:44.000Z","msg":"妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c17539e176c8cf269c9eb95f34791ffba72a718","tid":175911,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T23:15:35.000Z","msg":"呱呱叫<img src=\"/assets/f